        "category": "other"
      },
      {
        "text": "ZScaler Client Connector 4.7 and 4.8 on Microsoft Windows hard codes a domain used to retrieve proxy configuration information. An attacker with control of this domain could provide arbitrary proxy configurations and intercept, redirect or disrupt traffic.",
        "title": "Risk Evaluation",
        "category": "summary"
      },
      {
        "text": "Fixed in 4.7.0.141 and 4.8.0.63.",
        "title": "Recommended Practices",
        "category": "general"
      },
